Well, my main character is made of only 4 sprites when standing still now that I've used 8x16 sprites. He is 16 pixels wide and 32 tall. If I were to use 8x8, it would be 8 sprites, which seems like a really big waste. With 8x16 you just cut that in half.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=138">Celius</a> — Mon Dec 29, 2008 8:49 am</p><hr />
