Contra uses 8x16 sprites, and so does Smash TV.<br /><br />But if you're using 8x16 sprites, you also have either bigger game objects or more game objects, which tends to cancel out the CPU reduction.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Mon Dec 29, 2008 8:42 am</p><hr />
